<p>&ldquo;Let me see your hand,&rdquo; she says.</p>

<p>I show her my right hand. The nails are trimmed close, but there are a few ragged cuticles, an open bug bite I scratched too hard, and a paper cut over one knuckle.</p>

<p>&ldquo;Better use a glove this time,&rdquo; she says. &ldquo;I&rsquo;m at the tail end.&rdquo;</p>

<p>The latex gloves are in the top drawer of the night stand, along with the lubricant, the vibrators, the dildos, and the condoms. I put a glove on, squirt some lubricant onto the fingers.</p>

