<p>Two fingers effortlessly become three. I fuck her the way she likes it: slow and steady, in and out, a rhythm she can trust. Her legs start shaking, and I feel her vagina open with a whoosh.</p>

<p>&ldquo;Do you want four fingers?&rdquo;</p>

<p>&ldquo;I want your fist,&rdquo; she gasps.</p>

<p>I twist my hand so the fingers form a vertical line. I can&rsquo;t believe the room in here, soft and warm, open to receive me. I tell her this is sacred space; I have my hand in the holy place. Everything begins here. Everything.</p>

<p>She grabs my wrist and guides me deeper. More lubricant on the bridge of my thumb bone. The thumb is the tricky part; I don&rsquo;t want to hurt her.</p>

<p>I&rsquo;m in. I turn my hand gently, the way she taught me, fingers fanned out, fluttering against her walls, which shudder with tremors. Then I fold in one finger at a time until my fist is clenched. She grabs my free hand and presses it to her heart. Her orgasm is coiled deep inside her, and she&rsquo;s working to bring it forth, hanging suspended over the abyss.</p>

