<p>&ldquo;Timmy, listen: I think you need to see a doctor.&rdquo;</p>

<p>He starts shaking his head and moaning. &ldquo;Not the E-ward, man. I can&rsquo;t wait all fucking night on those plastic chairs they got.&rdquo;</p>

<p>I continue doggedly. &ldquo;The thing is, you were just saying how you wanted to go away, like Mark. That&rsquo;s like saying you want to kill yourself.&rdquo;</p>

<p>&ldquo;I did! But then I couldn&rsquo;t.&rdquo;</p>

<p>&ldquo;See, Timmy, that&rsquo;s serious. It&rsquo;s like part of you wants to kill yourself. But another part doesn&rsquo;t.&rdquo;</p>

